{"type":"message","id":"54577837","parentId":"856d52f3","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:25:28.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"小红书又不给我推\" which means \"Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book) isn't pushing me content again.\" This seems to be a complaint about the Xiaohongshu social media platform not showing them content in their feed.\n\nLet me check - this is Saturday, April 4th, 2026 at 12:25 GMT+8. According to HEARTBEAT.md, it's the weekend (周末 — 休息日，不打扰). So I should just respond naturally without triggering heartbeat rules.\n\nThe user seems to be talking about the Xiaohongshu app/platform not giving them content recommendations. I should respond conversationally about this."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 哈哈，小红书限流了吧？还是账号被降权了？😄\n\n你平时刷到啥内容比较多？我看看能不能帮你想想办法。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775276719462}}
