{"type":"message","id":"8b350f51","parentId":"7056f091","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:25:46.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is talking about my scheduled task for 小红书旅游热度每日推送. They're saying \"不是，你的定时任务\" meaning \"No, your scheduled task\" - they're asking about the 小红书定时推送任务.\n\nCurrent time is Saturday, April 4th, 2026 - it's the weekend. According to HEARTBEAT.md and my cron setup, the 小红书旅游热度每日推送 is set to run at 工作日 11:30 (weekdays at 11:30 AM). Since today is Saturday, the cron task wouldn't run.\n\nLet me check - the cron job I set up was for 工作日 11:30 (weekdays only), so it wouldn't run on weekends. The user seems to be expecting the push but it's not happening because it's Saturday.\n\n\nI should let them know that the推送 only runs on weekdays, not weekends."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 哦！那个小红书旅游热度推送？\n\n今天是周六，cron 设的是**工作日 11:30**，所以周末不会跑～\n\n要现在手动跑一次吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775276738550}}
