{"type":"message","id":"329917f8","parentId":"59033a9e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:27:35.768Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2syc7pb21xbg_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\ADHD_agent\\openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\r\nConfig warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\ADHD_agent\\openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\r\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) �?If it works, it's automation; if it breaks, it's a \"learning opportunity.\"\r\nUsage: openclaw cron edit [options] <id>\r\nEdit a cron job (patch fields)\r\nArguments:\r\n  id                                   Job id\r\nOptions:\r\n  --account <id>                       Channel account id for delivery\r\n                                       (multi-account setups)\r\n  --agent <id>                         Set agent id\r\n  --announce                           Announce summary to a chat\r\n                                       (subagent-style)\r\n  --at <when>                          Set one-shot time (ISO) or duration like\r\n                                       20m\r\n  --best-effort-deliver                Do not fail job if delivery fails\r\n  --channel <channel>                  Delivery channel (last)\r\n  --clear-agent                        Unset agent and use default (default:\r\n                                       false)\r\n  --clear-session-key                  Unset session key (default: false)\r\n  --cron <expr>                        Set cron expression\r\n  --delete-after-run                   Delete one-shot job after it succeeds\r\n                                       (default: false)\r\n  --deliver                            Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a\r\n                                       summary to a chat.\r\n  --description <text>                 Set description\r\n  --disable                            Disable job (default: false)\r\n  --enable                             Enable job (default: false)\r\n  --every <duration>                   Set interval duration like 10m\r\n  --exact                              Disable cron staggering (set stagger to\r\n                                       0)\r\n  --expect-final                       Wait for final response (agent) (default:\r\n                                       false)\r\n  --failure-alert                      Enable failure alerts for this job\r\n  --failure-alert-account-id <id>      Account ID for failure alert channel\r\n                                       (multi-account setups)\r\n  --failure-alert-after <n>            Alert after N consecutive job errors\r\n  --failure-alert-channel <channel>    Failure alert channel (last)\r\n  --failure-alert-cooldown <duration>  Minimum time between alerts (e.g. 1h,\r\n                                       30m)\r\n  --failure-alert-mode <mode>          Failure alert delivery mode (announce or\r\n                                       webhook)\r\n  --failure-alert-to <dest>            Failure alert destination\r\n  -h, --help                           Display help for command\r\n  --keep-after-run                     Keep one-shot job after it succeeds\r\n                                       (default: false)\r\n  --light-context                      Enable lightweight bootstrap context for\r\n                                       agent jobs\r\n  --message <text>                     Set agentTurn payload message\r\n  --model <model>                      Model override for agent jobs\r\n  --name <name>                        Set name\r\n  --no-best-effort-deliver             Fail job when delivery fails\r\n  --no-deliver                         Disable announce delivery\r\n  --no-failure-alert                   Disable failure alerts for this job\r\n  --no-light-context                   Disable lightweight bootstrap context for\r\n                                       agent jobs\r\n  --session <target>                   Session target (main|isolated)\r\n  --session-key <key>                  Set session key for job routing\r\n  --stagger <duration>                 Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\r\n  --system-event <text>                Set systemEvent payload\r\n  --thinking <level>                   Thinking level for agent jobs\r\n                                       (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\r\n  --timeout <ms>                       Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\r\n  --timeout-seconds <n>                Timeout seconds for agent jobs\r\n  --to <dest>                          Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram\r\n                                       chatId, or Discord channel/user)\r\n  --token <token>                      Gateway token (if required)\r\n  --tz <iana>                          Timezone for cron expressions (IANA)\r\n  --url <url>                          Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to\r\n                                       gateway.remote.url when configured)\r\n  --wake <mode>                        Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4380,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\ADHD_agent\\openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\r\nConfig warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\ADHD_agent\\openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\r\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) �?If it works, it's automation; if it breaks, it's a \"learning opportunity.\"\r\nUsage: openclaw cron edit [options] <id>\r\nEdit a cron job (patch fields)\r\nArguments:\r\n  id                                   Job id\r\nOptions:\r\n  --account <id>                       Channel account id 