{"type":"message","id":"4eaa5313","parentId":"9ddee048","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:28:14.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both cron jobs have been updated successfully. The schedule has been changed from `0 11 * * 1-5` (Mon-Fri) to `0 11 * * *` (every day).\n\nNow I can see the jobs are still showing errors with \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\" - this seems like a persistent issue with the delivery. But the user didn't ask about that, they just wanted the daily schedule.\n\nLet me confirm to the user that the change is done."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 搞定！两个任务都改成**每天 11:30**跑了：\n\n- ✅ 小红书旅游热度推送：`aa7a03fc` → `0 11 * * *`\n- ✅ 国际机票推送：`ed08c32f` → `0 11 * * *`\n\n另外注意到这两个任务最近都有推送失败的错误（`Delivering to Feishu requires target...`），看起来 delivery target 配置有问题。要不要一起看看？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775276888786}}
