{"type":"message","id":"22bd0467","parentId":"f7790ab8","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:28:30.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"机票也是\" (flight tickets too) - meaning the flight tracker push is also not working. This confirms what I already noticed - both tasks have delivery errors. The user seems to be acknowledging my point about the delivery target issue.\n\nBut they also seem to be saying they want the flight push to run daily too (which I already changed). Let me confirm this and then address the delivery error issue.\n\nWait, re-reading the conversation - I already changed the flight push cron to daily (`0 11 * * *`). The user is saying \"机票也是\" meaning the flight push task is also not working/not getting pushed. They want me to look at the delivery error issue.\n\n\nLooking at the job state, the delivery is set to `direct` mode on Feishu but the target format `user:ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b` appears to be incorrect, which is what's causing the delivery failures. I need to check the cron jobs.json file to verify the current configuration and fix this target format issue."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，我刚才也把机票推送改成每天了（`0 11 * * *`）。\n\n至于推送失败的问题——看错误信息是 delivery target 格式不对：\n\n```\nlastError: \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"\n```\n\n目标写的是 `user:ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b`，格式看起来是对的，但还是报错了。可能是飞书插件在 job delivery 里解析 `user:` 前缀的方式有问题。\n\n我来修一下，直接去掉 `user:` 前缀试试：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pe0pvq9kolj5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron edit aa7a03fc-d3f3-4670-a745-c28e1c28d810 --to \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\"","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":177527689