{"type":"message","id":"1895c679","parentId":"80b3e647","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:15:10.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron jobs show that:\n- `ed08c32f-6c5c-4...` (国际机票推送): 29h ago - last ran about 29 hours ago\n- `aa7a03fc-d3f3-4...` (旅游攻略汇总推送): 29h ago - last ran about 29 hours ago\n- `f988438d-d7a0-4...` (这个应该是 MEMORY.md 里的旧任务，旅游攻略每日推送): 12d ago\n\nWait, 29h ago from now (Saturday 16:14) would be... 16:14 on Friday minus 29 hours = about 11:14 on Friday. \n\nSo the jobs did run yesterday around 11:30, but they're showing errors. The \"29h ago\" timestamp makes sense since it's currently Saturday 16:14, which puts yesterday's run at roughly 11:14. The status indicator for unknown delivery status is puzzling given the job ID discrepancy and the fact that the feishu direct task had that delivery error, but I need to understand what that \"?\"% actually represents.\n\nThe real problem is the consecutive errors - both the 机票 and 旅游攻略 jobs are failing with the same delivery issue, yet they did execute yesterday. I should check the OpenClaw logs to see what's actually happening when these jobs run, or look at the delivery-queue directory to understand why the error keeps recurring.\n\nWait, I think I see the issue now - the delivery method is set to \"direct\" mode, which might not be the right approach for how this is supposed to work.\n\nLooking at the actual task states, the real problem seems to be that the jobs ran but failed to deliver properly. The `lastDeliveryStatus: \"unknown\"` combined with that error about needing a target suggests the delivery itself isn't configured correctly, not necessarily the schedule.\n\nI should test whether these jobs can actually execute successfully by running them manually rather than trying to parse more logs. But first, let me verify the gateway is functioning - it shows as connected locally on port 18790, so that's not the issue."},{"type":"text","text":"看到了：\n- 机票推送：29小时前跑了，但报 `unknown` 投递状态\n- 旅游攻略推送：29小时前跑了，同样失败\n- 还有一个 `f988438d`（旧版任务）：12天前\n\n现在的核心问题是：**任务触发了，但投递（delivery）失败**。我来测试一下现在能不能正常推送：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xob6jqbb8l2c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron trigger aa7a03fc-d3f3-4670-a745-c28e1c28d810 2>&1","yieldMs":8000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775290494381}}
