{"type":"message","id":"8cfcd77f","parentId":"4531ee23","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:16:31.477Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gmqy5t1hk7s1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"aa7a03fc-d3f3-4670-a745-c28e1c28d810\",\n      \"name\": \"旅游攻略汇总推送\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774323335662,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775185502621,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 11 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"请执行以下步骤推送小红书旅游内容：\\n1. 运行 python C:\\\\Users\\\\linkang\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\xiaohongshu_push_v3.py 获取今日小红书旅游热度内容和封面图\\n2. 读取运行结果（图片在 C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\uploads\\\\push_1.jpg ~ push_5.jpg）\\n3. 把内容+封面图一起推送到飞书，每条笔记发一条消息（文字+对应图片）\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"direct\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"target\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775358000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775185200014,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 302607,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 4,\n        \"lastError\": \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ed08c32f-6c5c-4300-b0fd-e1cd974735fc\",\n      \"name\": \"国际机票推送\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774326644918,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775276888474,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 11 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"请执行以下步骤推送国际机票日报：\\n1. 运行 exec: python C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\ctrip_tracker.py --direct\\n2. 读取脚本的控制台输出作为推送文案\\n3. 读取 C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\uploads\\\\flight_trend.png 作为趋势图\\n4. 把文案和趋势图一起发送到飞书\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"direct\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"target\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775358000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775187000018,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 603393,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 4,\n        \"lastError\": \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"rules-refresh-daily\",\n      \"name\": \"Cursor协作规则刷新\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774862400000,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775264524213,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\\n\\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\\npython \\\"C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\.cursor\\\\skills\\\\async-notify\\\\scripts\\\\submit_task.py\\\" --title \\\"任务标题\\\" --instructions \\\"具体指令\\\" --submitted-by \\\"OpenClaw\\\" --notify\\n\\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\\npython \\\"C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\.cursor\\\\skills\\\\async-notify\\\\scripts\\\\confirm_write.py\\\" --task-id \\\"task_id\\\" --decision auto --reply \\\"用户回复原文\\\"\\n\\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\\npython \\\"C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\.cursor\\\\skills\\\\async-notify\\\\scripts\\\\submit_task.py\\\" --list\\n\\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\\npython \\\"C:\\\\ADHD_agent\\\\.cursor\\\\skills\\\\async-notify\\\\scripts\\\\submit_task.py\\\" --results\\n\\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"silent\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"target\": \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 5,\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775350800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775264400016,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 124197,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"lastError\": \"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775290591473}}
